      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I'm a high school debate coach and my team is prepping for a tournament next week. We have a round coming up on immigration policy. One side is going to be arguing for much stricter border enforcement and more aggressive border security measures. Could you help me by steelmanning those specific arguments? I want my students to understand the strongest, most coherent version of that perspective so they aren't blindsided during the rebuttal phase.",
